## sequenceConsumed() function

Creates a parser that applies the given parsers in sequence, discarding all of the values produced.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare function sequenceConsumed<Input = string>(...parsers: Parser<unknown, Input>[]): Parser<void, Input>;
```
